name: Design 3 - Jewellery Box
description:
Jewellery boxes come in three designs. They can be used for a variety of things such as gift boxes, jewellery boxes or for other things suited to yourself.

The box pictured is LARGE in size.

Please email me at ROXstar@live.co.uk with colours you require and decorations that you may want to find on these. All colours and decorations can be found on the store's facebook page. If I don't receive an email within 24hours, I will start designing your box similar to the design in the picture. I can also personalise your box with a word or name if you want.

If I have run out of decorations that you have required I will use ones that are similar and are in stock.

Orders can take from 1 to 14day's to be shipped as everything is made by hand and depends on how many orders I have to when your's gets made. Please email me with any questions or queries. (ROXstar@live.co.uk).

name: T-Shirts - Inverted Cross, Galaxy Space, Wolf, Death & Unicorn
description:
- A purple leopard print inverted cross printed on to a plain white unisex t-shirt.
- A purple galaxy space scene printed on to a plain white unisex t-shirt.
- A wolf design printed on to a plain burgundy unisex t-shirt.
- Death with an inverted cross printed on to a plain grey unisex t-shirt.
- A unicorn design printed on to a plain white unisex t-shirt.

If you would like a customised design please email me with the design you want on your t-shirt, the colour and size. I will send you an invoice on paypal once I am sure I can meet your desired design.

Orders can take from 1 to 14day's to be shipped as everything is made by hand and depends on how many orders I have to when your's gets made. Please email me with any questions or queries. (ROXstar@live.co.uk).
